*Probudio* se u ranu zoru. (He woke up early in the morning.)
*Njegov glas je *probudio* me iz sna. (His voice woke me up from my sleep.)
*Njegov šapat je *probudio* nadu u njenoj duši. (His whisper woke up hope in her soul.)
*Krik njegovog deteta ga je *probudio*. (The cry of his child woke him up.)
*Njegov zvižduk je *probudio* ptice. (His whistle woke up the birds.)